.TH "of_scan_pci_bridge" 9 "of_scan_pci_bridge" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
of_scan_pci_bridge \- Set up a PCI bridge and scan for child nodes
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" of_scan_pci_bridge
.BI "(struct pci_dev *dev "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
pci_dev structure for the bridge
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
\fBof_scan_bus\fP calls this routine for each PCI bridge that it finds, and
this routine in turn call \fBof_scan_bus\fP recusively to scan for more child
devices.
